从前有一个很漂亮的女孩叫做 仙杜瑞拉，
他有一个继母 和 两个心底恶毒的姐姐，
她的两个姐姐和继母 让她做 所有的脏活累活，不停地虐待她。

once upon a time there was a beautiful girl named Cinderella who lived with
her stepmother and two wicked sisters who always forcing her to do all the dirty work.

王子要举办舞会，邀请城里年轻的女孩都去参加，
继母不允许灰姑娘去，而是让她在家里干活。

one day, the prince of the country was planning to have a dancing party and
invited all young girls in the city to attend.
The stepmother didn't want Cinderella go out to join the party but to work at home.

灰姑娘在仙女的帮助下有了礼服和水晶鞋，但是有个条件，必须在12点之前回家。
With the help of the fairy, Cinderella got the dress and crystal shoes she need,
but she must return home before twelve o'clock at night as the fairy asked.

舞会上，灰姑娘和王子跳舞，互生爱意。
舞会的最后一天，灰姑娘在匆忙之中 将水晶鞋落在了皇宫。
At the party, Cinderella had a dance with the prince and they fell in love with each other
immediately.
when the clock was about to strike 12 o'clock midnight, Cinderella dropped
王子派人寻找水晶鞋的主人，说谁能穿上这只鞋子，谁就是她的新娘。
最后灰姑娘穿进了鞋子，成为王子的新娘，过上了幸福快乐的生活。